NOTICE

This software uses data from SINAN/DATASUS (Brazilian Ministry of Health).
The data is publicly available and used for educational and research purposes.

DISCLAIMER

This system is a SUPPORT TOOL for clinical decision-making. It does NOT:
- Replace medical evaluation
- Make definitive diagnoses
- Replace complementary exams
- Substitute qualified healthcare professionals

Medical supervision is MANDATORY. The authors are not responsible for 
clinical decisions made based on this system.

For medical emergencies, always seek immediate professional care.
